<section class="av_textblock_section "  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class='avia_textblock  '   itemprop="text" ><p><strong>Antragstermine für die Projektförderung</strong></p>
<p>2.  Antragstermin 2020:    <strong>1.11.<br />
</strong>1.  Antragstermin  2021:<strong>    2.5.</strong></p>
</div></section></div></div></div><div class="flex_cell no_margin av_one_third  avia-builder-el-37  el_after_av_cell_one_third  el_before_av_cell_one_third   "  style='background: #f2f2f2; vertical-align:top; padding:10px; background-color:#f2f2f2; ' ><div class='flex_cell_inner' >
<div class="flex_column av_one_full  flex_column_div first  avia-builder-el-38  avia-builder-el-no-sibling  " style='background: #f2f2f2; padding:20px 10px 0px 10px ; background-color:#f2f2f2; border-radius:0px; '><section class="av_textblock_section "  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class='avia_textblock  '   itemprop="text" ><h2 style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;"><strong><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-4081" src="https://bundesstiftung-friedensforschung.de/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dsffirst40.png" alt="Auf dem Bild ist das Logo der Stiftung in klein abgebildet." width="40" height="29" />Ende Post-Doc</strong></span></h2>
